data.description: Possible assumable 2.25% VA Loan, subject to lender approval. Far lower than today's market rates! Spacious home with amazing views close to town! 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom, 3100Sqft home on 2.34 acres with views of Pend Oreille Lake and River, Schweitzer and Sandpoint itself! Main floor features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a great room with open concept kitchen, dining and living room. Livingroom area includes gas fireplace, stone hearth and wood mantel. Dining room leads out onto the porch, enjoy the views! Nicely appointed kitchen with stainless steel appliances, gas stove, large island with bar seating, and pantry. Main floor master with en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. Lower level features family room, 2 bedrooms, a bathroom and laundry room combo, storage room and lots of closets. Lower level family room opens onto patio and hot tub area. Includes attached finished 2-car garage. All of this less than a 10 min drive to Sandpoint!
